## 🌐 Environment Variables

### `Backend/.env`

```env
# Server
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=development

# Database
MONGO_URI=mongodb+srv://...

# Auth
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_min_32_chars
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d

# CORS (set to your Vercel URL in production)
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:5173

# Escalation thresholds
ESCALATE_L1_HOURS=48
ESCALATE_L2_HOURS=72
ESCALATION_CRON_MINUTES=60
```

### `Frontend/.env`

```env
# Development — Vite proxy handles /api routing, relative URL works everywhere
VITE_API_URL=/api

# Production — override this in your Vercel dashboard, don't commit it
# VITE_API_URL=https://civic-connect-4w0n.onrender.com/api
```

