## 🐛 Troubleshooting

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| `Failed to fetch` on login | Make sure the backend is running on port 5000 |
| `MongoServerError` on startup | Check your `MONGO_URI` in `Backend/.env` |
| `EADDRINUSE :5000` | Run `npx kill-port 5000` then retry |
| `EADDRINUSE :5173` | Run `npx kill-port 5173` then retry |
| Issues load but login fails | Hard-refresh the browser (`Ctrl + Shift + R`) |
| Vercel shows 404 on refresh | Add `vercel.json` with the SPA rewrite rule above |
| Render API returns CORS error | Set `CLIENT_URL` to your exact Vercel URL in Render env vars |

